quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  7,105,"No haand i e am nde mi wowlataa e Alla si wanaa goonga. GooŇč…óii mi addanii on …ďanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mon. neldu e …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen."
  7,106,"[Fir'awna] wi'i : "Si tawii a ardii e maande, addu nde si tawii ko a jeyaa…óo e gooŇč…óuu…ďe …ďeen"."
  7,107,"O wernii weduru makko ndun, jaka ko ndu mboo…ódi=ngoolwa …ďanngundi."
  7,108,"O yaltini junngo makko ngon, jaka yoo ko ngo ranwungo wonannde ndaaroo…ďe …ďen."
  7,109,"Mbatu yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďen mbi'i : "Pellet, oo, ko mbileejo ganndu…óo"."
  7,110,""O faala yaltinnde on ka leydi mo'on". -"Ko hol…óum njamirton?""
  7,111,"∆Āe mbi'i : "Nee…ďnu mo e musi…ó…óo makko on, nulaa e ce'e …óeen moo…ďoo…ďe (mbile)".wilee…ďe"
  7,112,"∆Āe ngadane kala mbileejo ganndu…óo."
  7,113,"wilee…ďe …ďeen ari Fir'awna …ďe mbi'i : "Hara njo…ďdi no woodani min, si min ngonii fool…ďe …ďeen?""
  7,114,"O wi'i : "Eyyo, haray on jeyaama e …ďa…ótinaa…ďe …ďeen"."
  7,115,"∆Āe mbi'i : "eehe yma Muusaa, si …óa yi…ói ko nde bugoto…óaa, maa men wona (adotoo…ďe) bugagol".(beddagol)"
  7,116,"O maaki : "Bugee(mbedde)". Nde …ďe bugii, (mbeddi )…ďe mbil…óii gite yim…ďe …ďeen, …ďe kul…ďini …ďe, …ďe ngddi mbilewu mawnungu."
  7,117,"minn mbahyini e Muusaa won de : "Bugo tuggordu maa ndun weduru". Jaka yoo hindi mo…óa ko …ďe pepekindotonoo."
  7,118,"Goonga on fee√Īi, ko …ďe ngollaynoo kon [fof] boni."
  7,119,"∆Āe poolaa …óoon …ďe kooti ko …ďe ja'asu…ďe."
  7,120,"Wilee…ďe …ďeen nduuyi cujji."